name: Supervised
description: In self, the dominance of the eyes cannot be separated from the beauty of beauty that stimulates the brain to be enjoyed or to think. But what can I do, sometimes it's different in the eyes, different in the heart, and vice versa. but after all, it's not just the eyes, just the brain and the heart, they are all fused like water, earth and air, in symbiosis with each other.
